0---o---o---------o-------------------+
    |   |         |
1---o---|-o---o---|-o-------------o---+
        | |   |   | |             |
2---o---o-|---o---|-|-o-----o-----o---+
    |     |       | | |     |      
3---o-----o-------|-|-|-o---|-o---o---+
                  | | | |   | |   |
4---o---o---------o-|-|-|---o-|---o---+
    |   |           | | |     |
5---o---|-o---o-----o-|-|-----o---o---+
        | |   |       | |         |
6---o---o-|---o-------o-|---------o---+
    |     |             |
7---o-----o-------------o-------------+

After the C series, the upper and lower sets of 4 are each in order.
The D, E and F series ensure that the sets of 8 are in order.

